    "title": "LinkedIn Optimization Secrets That Get You Noticed",
    "excerpt": "LinkedIn Optimization Secrets That Get You Noticed LinkedIn is much more than an online resume—it's your professional stage where you can showcase your skills, experience, and personality to attract recruiters and opp…",
    "category": "Career Development",
    "readTime": "4 min read",
