    "title": "Remote Work Skills Every Professional Needs to Master",
    "excerpt": "Remote Work Skills Every Professional Needs to Master Remote work has become a major part of the modern workplace, especially in recent years. Many companies offer flexible or fully remote jobs, giving employees the f…",
    "category": "Career Advice",
    "readTime": "4 min read",
    "date": "August 9, 2025",
