    "title": "Top 10 Skills That Will Make You Recession-Proof",
    "excerpt": "Top 10 Skills That Will Make You Recession-Proof In today’s fast-changing world, we never know when the economy might slow down or a recession might hit. During such times, having the right skills can be the differenc…",
    "category": "Career Advice",
